{"title":"In the Drops: The Maurice Burton Way, Jelenew kit, Sloggi shorts and Grand Theft Auto","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/maurice-burton-way-book","date":1714131681000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/maurice-burton-way-book\">In the Drops: The Maurice Burton Way, Jelenew kit, Sloggi shorts and Grand Theft Auto</a></p>\n\n<p>Happy Friday! I’m here to delight you with another edition of <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/in-the-drops\" target=\"_blank\">In the Drops</a>. But aside from that, it’s been a busy week at <em>Cyclist</em> (as per usual).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/la-vuelta-femenina-preview\" target=\"_blank\">La Vuelta Femenina</a> will run from 28th April to the 5th May, with a fierce field containing Demi Vollering (SD Worx-Protime), Kasia Niewiadoma (Canyon-SRAM), Elisa Longo Borghini and Gaia Realini (Lidl-Trek). The first men’s Grand Tour of the year is almost here too, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/giro-ditalia-watch-live-stages-route-riders-teams-start-list\" target=\"_blank\">the Giro d’Italia</a> will begin on 4th May with <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/tadej-pogacar\" target=\"_blank\">Tadej Pogačar</a> (UAE Team Emirates) the man to beat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For all your bike concerns, we’ve got new buyer’s guides on the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-cycling-socks-for-summer\" target=\"_blank\">best socks for summer</a> (even though the weather disagrees) and the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-energy-drinks-cycling\" target=\"_blank\">best energy drink powders</a>, plus tutorials including how to <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/how-to-breathe-better-on-a-bike\" target=\"_blank\">breathe better on the bike</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tutorials/should-you-sit-or-stand-when-climbing\" target=\"_blank\">whether you should sit or stand when climbing</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ewan has broken the internet with his article on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/opinion-mens-cycling-2024\" target=\"_blank\">predictability of men’s cycling</a> lately and has collated all the bigger <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cycling-transfer-rumours\" target=\"_blank\">cycling transfer rumours</a> like a pro. Speaking of, have you welcomed the newbies <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/author/ewan-wilsonmetropolis-co-uk\" target=\"_blank\">Ewan Wilson</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/author/laurence-kilpatrick\" target=\"_blank\">Laurence Kilpatrick</a> to the team yet?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alright, let’s get cracking.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/opinion-mens-cycling-2024\">Opinion: Men’s cycling has never been more bleak for fans</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/maurice-burton-podcast\">Cyclist Magazine Podcast episode 101: Maurice Burton, the original British track legend</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/la-vuelta-femenina-preview\">La Vuelta Femenina 2024: Route, how to watch, start list and everything you need to know</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/giro-ditalia-watch-live-stages-route-riders-teams-start-list\">Giro d’Italia 2024: Stage-by-stage preview and how to watch</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>The Maurice Burton Way by Maurice Burton and Paul Jones</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-2048x1365.jpeg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-8-350x233.jpeg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/the-story-of-maurice-burton-britain-s-first-black-cycling-champion\" target=\"_blank\">Maurice Burton</a> Way is a phenomenal autobiography, written by the man himself alongside Phil Jones. It goes in depth into the life of Britain’s first black cycling champion – who once stepped onto the podium in 1974 to boos from the crowd – and his journey from the child of a Windrush generation father to the Commonwealth Games, experiencing racism, living to Belgium and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The book also covers Burton’s post-racing career running <a href=\"https://www.devercycles.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">De Ver Cycles</a> in south London. It’s an enthralling and necessary read.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/maurice-burton-podcast\" target=\"_blank\">our podcast with Burton</a> too, where he recalls some of the highlights from the book including his time competing in 56 Six-Day races and experiencing sabotage.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy a signed hardback copy now from <a href=\"https://www.devercycles.co.uk/dpt/pgr/the-maurice-burton-way-personally-signed-hardcover-britains-first-black-cycling-champion__69265\" target=\"_blank\">De Ver Cycles (£20)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jelenew kit</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hourglass Short Sleeve Jersey</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2-350x233.jpeg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-2.jpeg 1566w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Hourglass short sleeve jersey from Jelenew has streamlined side panels and is made for riding in hotter weather. I like the two different coloured sleeves to give it a funky look. However, as someone with a bigger chest, the contour design probably pulls too much focus to the chest area. Jelenew products are thinner/smaller than most cycling kits and more expensive.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jelenew.com%2Fen-gb%2Fproducts%2Fhourglass-short-sleeve-jersey-zepher%3Fjelenew_id%3D787b303e51edebf87b3b37beee91e75a%26distinct_id%3D18f14de10438a1-09f83440e53dbc-1b525637-1296000-18f14de104456e\" target=\"_blank\">Jelenew (£108)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Avant Sleeveless Mesh Base Layer</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-2048x1365.jpeg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-3-350x233.jpeg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>An essential in everyone’s wardrobe. A good <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/should-you-still-wear-a-base-layer-in-the-summer\" target=\"_blank\">base layer</a> is key in regulating temperature and wicking moisture from the skin. This Avant Sleeveless Mesh Base Layer is an ideal thinness and keeps sweat from overwhelming your jersey.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Size up if you have a bigger chest.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jelenew.com%2Fen-gb%2Fproducts%2Fbase-layer-women-1%3Fjelenew_id%3D787b303e51edebf87b3b37beee91e75a%26distinct_id%3D18f14de10438a1-09f83440e53dbc-1b525637-1296000-18f14de104456e\" target=\"_blank\">Jelenew (£99)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>L’avenir Long Sleeve Jersey</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4-350x233.jpeg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-4.jpeg 1626w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed for windy or warmer days from 15C-25C, the L’avenir jersey has long sleeves but is thin enough that it can be used to layer up.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5-350x233.jpeg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-5.jpeg 1416w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Jelenew says the back pocket is ‘anti-sag’. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jelenew.com%2Fen-gb%2Fproducts%2Flavenir-long-sleeve-jersey-2%3Fjelenew_id%3D787b303e51edebf87b3b37beee91e75a%26distinct_id%3D18f14de10438a1-09f83440e53dbc-1b525637-1296000-18f14de104456e\" target=\"_blank\">Jelenew (£294)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Evolve Y Back Bib Shorts 8”</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-2048x1365.jpeg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-7-350x233.jpeg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Evolve Y Back Bib Shorts are made of moisture-wicking fabric for hot days and designed with an aerodynamic fit in mind. The moulded chamois is one of the more padded ones I have come across too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-2048x1365.jpeg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-750x500.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-1140x760.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-6-350x233.jpeg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They sit at 8” with a silicone leg gripper to keep the shorts in place.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=205647X1684865&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jelenew.com%2Fen-gb%2Fproducts%2Fevolve-y-back-bib-shorts%3Fjelenew_id%3D787b303e51edebf87b3b37beee91e75a%26distinct_id%3D18f14de10438a1-09f83440e53dbc-1b525637-1296000-18f14de104456e\" target=\"_blank\">Jelenew (£249)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sloggi Ever Infused Shorts</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-10-970x647.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/04/Robyn-In-the-Drops-10-970x646.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/s